A video which shows a group of four men unloading a truck on Oxford Street as it slowly made its way through traffic has been shared widely on social media. In the video, taken by a driver following the truck in East London s main street, a man is seen climbing on the back of the heavy goods truck and stealing a pack of two-litre drinks. After he gets off another hops on to the truck and takes three packets of the drink handing them over to his friends. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share